commits.message:
Merge pull request #3 from bricktrooper/objectDetectionTest

Launch storyboard added

Add Python script for SpatialSense on Raspberry Pi

This script can be run on the Raspberry Pi Zero using
Python. The speaker will beep when the user crosses
the threshold distance to any object in front of them.
The rate of the beeping will increase as the user gets
closer to the object.

AwareApp object detection

Add final code for AwareApp, an iOS app that is able to help the 
visually impaired with object recognition.
